question.introduction:
Handling and storing data go hand in hand. As a micro or small business you are also concerned with this. As it is the case
for nearly all companies, it is very likely your company holds sensitive data that needs to be kept safe from attacks,
theft or unwarranted access. Thus, it is important to store this information securely.

